quote.nm: Grand Talents Group Holdings Ltd. - Rights
quote.summary: Grand Talents Group Holdings Ltd is an investment holding company principally engaged in maintenance engineering business. The Company operates its business through two segments. The Repair and Maintenance Works segment provides repair and maintenance works for structures of roads and highways. The repair and maintenance works for structures include routine cleansing and inspection; replacement and repair works of highway; replacement, repair and demolition of road signs; painting and application of protective coating; and concrete pavement and repair, among others. In addition, it also provides regional works. The Civil Engineering Construction Works segment provides civil engineering construction works of road and highway related infrastructures. The civil engineering construction works include demolition works, site formation, construction of foundation of lift towers, shelter for footbridges, construction of structure and installation of pipes.
